  <!-- TECHNICAL NOTES -->
  <h2>Technical implementation notes</h2>
  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Data model (per practice)</h4>
      <ul style="font-size:0.875rem;padding-left:1rem">
        <li>id, name, tagline, founded_year</li>
        <li>address, lat/lng, phone, website</li>
        <li>specialties[] (general, pedo, ortho, perio, etc.)</li>
        <li>languages[] (en, es, etc.)</li>
        <li>hours_by_day, accepting_new_patients, emergency_avail</li>
        <li>plans[] (name, price, benefits[], featured)</li>
        <li>features[] (open_weekends, sunbit_financing, etc.)</li>
        <li>rating, review_count (from Google + Clerri)</li>
        <li>premium_tier (boolean — affects placement)</li>
        <li>total_active_members (anonymized)</li>
        <li>logo_url, hero_image_url, gallery[]</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Build complexity breakdown</h4>
      <ul style="font-size:0.875rem;padding-left:1rem">
        <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> ~4-6 weeks (Next.js or Astro static + dynamic search). Could be built faster with Lovable for MVP.</li>
        <li><strong>Practice profile pages:</strong> ~2-3 weeks (5,000 dynamic pages auto-generated).</li>
        <li><strong>Backend / data sync:</strong> ~4-8 weeks (Salesforce → directory schema, nightly sync, image hosting).</li>
        <li><strong>Mapbox or Google Maps integration:</strong> ~1-2 weeks (Mapbox is cheaper at scale).</li>
        <li><strong>SEO scaffolding:</strong> 5,000+ city pages + 5,000 practice pages → schema.org + sitemap.</li>
        <li><strong>Compliance review:</strong> 2-4 weeks (DMPO state-by-state for consumer-facing claims).</li>
        <li><strong>Total v1:</strong> ~12-16 weeks. MVP scope can ship in 8 weeks.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Practice-side monetization tiers</h4>
      <ul style="font-size:0.875rem;padding-left:1rem">
        <li><strong>Free (default):</strong> All Clerri-member practices listed automatically. Standard card. Profile page.</li>
        <li><strong>Premium ($X/mo):</strong> Featured placement in search results. Photo gallery on profile. Lead capture form. Analytics dashboard (who viewed your listing, who clicked-to-call).</li>
        <li><strong>Enterprise (DSO-tier):</strong> Multi-location aggregated profile. DSO-level analytics. Co-branded landing pages per location.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Patient acquisition funnel</h4>
      <ul style="font-size:0.875rem;padding-left:1rem">
        <li>Patient searches Google for "affordable dentist near me"</li>
        <li>Lands on Clerri city page (SEO-optimized)</li>
        <li>Filters by their preferences (price, distance, language)</li>
        <li>Clicks practice profile</li>
        <li>Either books appointment OR clicks "Join membership"</li>
        <li>Conversion event tracked + attributed to Clerri</li>
        <li>Practice receives lead notification</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

